      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three mesh levels; GCI 3.2% on NIH at design point. Formal observed order of accuracy is 1.7 (slightly below theoretical 2nd order), attributed to near-wall mesh non-uniformity in volute region. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
