    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed. Seven factors were assessed with achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5; six factors were not assessed due to resource and data constraints. Monte Carlo UQ was performed covering primary uncertainty sources. The assessment team accepts this package as documenting the current credibility state, acknowledging that the decision outcome reflects acceptance of the assessment process rather than acceptance of the model for regulatory submission. Experimental comparison results confirm model predictions are within 11.4% MAE of FDA benchmark data.",
